snippet.title: Puzzles For Yoshis Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Yoshi awakes in a strange cold chamber. He is forced to go through several puzzles. This hack was made around 2019/2020 between Indigo Island and Flower Cup. I did make a trailer for F4, but it's currently on my dead laptop. Might got hunting for it off Kaze's channel. There are ~20 puzzles with 39 stars.
